---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="InterStellar AI">
  <section class="hero-b">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">✶ interstellarai.net · est. 2026</div>
          <h1>Small software, <em>shipped</em> by machines.</h1>
          <p class="lede">A portfolio of tiny AI-powered tools — and the engineering handbook that keeps them shipping. Automation drafts the PRs. Staging gates the deploys. Humans write the ADRs and drink the coffee.</p>
          <div class="ctas">
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-md" href="/projects">See the projects →</a>
            <a class="btn btn-link btn-md" href="/tenets">Read the tenets</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-meta">
            <span>◉ 5 repos in orbit</span>
            <span>✶ 4 ADRs, counting</span>
            <span>· auto-deployed</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="diagram">
          <img src="/assets/illustration-orbit.svg" alt="" class="drift"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="how">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="how-cell">
        <div class="num">◯ 01</div>
        <h3>A human writes <em>an intent.</em></h3>
        <p>A GitHub issue, a two-line prose spec, or a sticky note. The bar is low; the point is to start.</p>
        <div class="links"><a href="/tenets">Why we write things down →</a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="how-cell">
        <div class="num">◯ 02</div>
        <h3>A <em>small tool</em> drafts the PR.</h3>
        <p>A YAML-driven harness turns the intent into a PR: scoped, CI-green, auto-merge armed.</p>
        <div class="links"><a href="/decisions/004-archon-drives-automation">ADR-004: one tool drives the portfolio →</a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="how-cell">
        <div class="num">◯ 03</div>
        <h3>Staging <em>is the gate.</em></h3>
        <p>Merges roll to staging, E2E runs, prod promotes if the gate passes. A fourth cron watches the first three.</p>
        <div class="links"><a href="/decisions/001-staging-before-prod">ADR-001 · ADR-002 →</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="portfolio">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2 class="section-title">What's <em>in orbit</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="portfolio-grid">
        <a class="pf-card" href="https://filmduel.interstellarai.net">
          <div class="row">
            <p class="name"><em>Film</em>Duel</p>
            <span class="badge badge-live">live</span>
          </div>
          <p class="blurb">Rank movies and TV via ELO duels.</p>
          <div class="foot"><span>FastAPI · React</span><span>↗</span></div>
        </a>
        <a class="pf-card" href="https://github.com/alexsiri7/Reli">
          <div class="row">
            <p class="name">Reli</p>
            <span class="badge badge-wip">wip</span>
          </div>
          <p class="blurb">Personal AI assistant with a knowledge graph.</p>
          <div class="foot"><span>FastAPI · React</span><span>↗</span></div>
        </a>
        <a class="pf-card" href="https://github.com/alexsiri7/word-coach-annie">
          <div class="row">
            <p class="name"><em>Word Coach</em> Annie</p>
            <span class="badge badge-wip">wip</span>
          </div>
          <p class="blurb">AI writing assistant for novelists.</p>
          <div class="foot"><span>Next.js · Supabase</span><span>↗</span></div>
        </a>
        <div class="pf-card">
          <div class="row">
            <p class="name"><em>Cosmic</em> Match</p>
            <span class="badge badge-wip">wip</span>
          </div>
          <p class="blurb">Space-themed match-3 mobile game.</p>
          <div class="foot"><span>Flutter · Flame</span><span></span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pf-card">
          <div class="row">
            <p class="name">The <em>Un-Reminder</em></p>
            <span class="badge badge-wip">wip</span>
          </div>
          <p class="blurb">Stochastic, context-aware habit prompts.</p>
          <div class="foot"><span>Android · on-device AI</span><span></span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
